title: Despite series loss, India retain second spot in latest ICC ODI rankings
text: Despite series loss, India retain second spot in latest ICC ODI rankings Monday, 26 October 2015 (1 minute ago) Virat Kohli rose up a rung to second in the batsmen's table of the latest ICC ODI cricket rankings issued on Monday.
